<plot>The last of the three-reel (27 minutes) western shorts made by Robert Emmett Tansey starring Wally Wales. Here, Jeff Smith and his horse, Silver King the Wonder Horse, arrive on the scene in time to give "Dad" Gray and his daughter, Dot, a helping hand in their fight against Gore and his henchmen, Wilson and Barney, in their effort to take over Gray's gold mine.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?571966</url></doc>
